  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2017-06-08T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Methane Emissions Mitigation Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Energy (DOE)to perform research and develop technology in methane leak detection and mitigation.\n\nDOE must also establish a technology clearinghouse for public access to information relating to technologies and best practices for methane leak detection and mitigation."
